  renderPathForWeight(weight, color, pathsByWeight);

const Percent = forwardRef<SVGSVGElement, IconProps>((props, ref) => (
  <IconBase ref={ref} {...props} renderPath={renderPath} />
));

Percent.displayName = "Percent";

export default Percent;
